{"tw": {"3412290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "NTR狂熱", "steam_appid": 3412290, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4234740], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟故事簡介💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為經濟狀況所困的新婚夫妻—千穗與翔太，偶然間成為了「你」，少房東龍之介新的房客。千穗與翔太是從大學就開始交往，新婚的生活每天都充滿了甜蜜。儘管翔太在工作上頻頻碰壁，兩人還是用微薄的薪水相依為命。當千穗出現在你的門口時，你立刻被她那碩大的胸部，完美的身體曲線，還有一看就未經世事的單純笑容給搞得血脈噴張。於是在小夫妻因為聽到房租價格而卻步時，你主動提出了一個方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「不如就讓千穗打掃我的房間，來彌補不足的租金吧。」一個大膽的計畫，就此展開。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而小夫妻的感情非常堅貞，一下子號稱是「超級種馬」的你竟然也不知道從何下手。於是你召喚出了早已看純潔的千穗不順眼很久的魅魔莉莉絲，與莉莉絲達成了一個交易。。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90天的倒數，從現在開始……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟遊戲內容💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一開始只是單純的上門打掃，把握每一次的相處，從言語調戲，到使用魅魔的力量，遠距離愛撫，一步一步累積千穗的慾望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當千穗情慾高漲，就可以更進一步進攻。隨著墮落能量逐漸累積，不只可以開啟新的魅魔技能和玩法，也可以看到千穗越來越克制不住自己的慾望，開始變得越來越主動。直到一切已經一發不可收拾……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著千穗的墮落階段不斷推進，還會開啟夜市、居酒屋、温泉旅館等不同場景。千穗也會開始傳一些充滿誘惑的自拍照給你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟遊戲玩法💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在90天內讓女主角墮落的模擬遊戲。遊戲每天分為早上、下午、晚上、午夜四個時段，每個時段可選擇不同行動，如打工賺錢、與女主角互動、購買道具等。包含多種小遊戲（如猜拳、送貨、射擊等），來推進親密度與劇情進展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/26f3bb02ab602966d7ea328c800bfa60.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 /></