873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/a6d2f0acc5cabf6b0eadb78c6423e3a2.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/a6d2f0acc5cabf6b0eadb78c6423e3a2.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/458ab18539e0857593eaaa6219168603.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/458ab18539e0857593eaaa6219168603.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/458ab18539e0857593eaaa6219168603.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過打工賺錢，可以購買更多推進劇情的強力道具。例如「針孔攝影機」能偷窺隔壁小夫妻的房間、「忍者捲軸」可以開啟特殊玩法。而隨著千穗的墮落能量不斷累積，玩家可以解鎖更多魅魔技能，開啟更多互動與劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/cfa1047ba9e75ab3ed66047b2a715a50.avif?t=1776137873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras_big/cfa1047ba9e75ab3ed66047b2a715a50.webp?t=1776137873 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/bf14377fa6d2325946096ddc76533234.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=2773 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/cb9a332e1a7ea5c30a4d5e3983b666f3.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/4671d8f7f2ca8c03ccb927dfcfb60832.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p>", "short_description": "為經濟狀況所困的新婚夫妻—千穗與翔太，偶然間成為了「你」，少房東龍之介新的房客。在小夫妻因為聽到房租價格而卻步時，你主動提出了一個方案。「不如就讓千穗打掃我的房間，來彌補不足的租金吧。」一個大膽的計畫，就此展開。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/37034e653b32fa93027e667ff59be8e8a92dcd5e/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776137873", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/a6151e4c83c57250e908405bda06d1c4e85a175b/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776137873", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/a6151e4c83c57250e908405bda06d1c4e85a175b/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776137873", "website": "https://x.com/tiramisuloventr", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 6 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 6 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["Tiramisu", "Big S Studio"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 28900, "final": 26000, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 289", "final_formatted": "NT$ 260"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}, {"id": "2", "description": "策略"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 12 月 17 日"}}}}, "us": {"3412290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "NTRaholic", "steam_appid": 3412290, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4234740], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f4141ebe70e4b7182357d9d45ab95b3c.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1560 height=1040 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟Story💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Ryunosuke, a young landlord, and you've just leased your property out to a newlywed couple. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chiho and Shota have been together since university. While Shota keeps hitting walls at work, only bringing home a modest income, the couple support each other and do their best to enjoy their sweet newlywed life. However, you can feel your heart pounding and blood rushing the moment you set eyes on Chiho. You’re struck by her voluptuous bust, perfectly curvy figure, and her innocent untainted smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the couple hesitates after hearing the rent amount, you casually make a bold proposal: “How about letting Chiho clean my room to make up for the rent difference?” The couple agrees, and your daring arrangement begins to unfold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite having been called the &quot;legendary seducer&quot;, the bond between Chiho and Shota holds firm. At a loss, you turn to Lilith, a mischievous succubus who has long been irritated by Chiho’s naive purity and together, you strike a pact. With Lilith’s magic, you’ll attempt to awaken Chiho’s suppressed desires over 90 days, guiding her on a journey where pleasure and temptation blur the line between loyalty and lust.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And so, the 90-day countdown begins...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟Features💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What begins as a simple housekeeping visit soon becomes something far more intimate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take every chance to interact with Chiho! Start with playful teasing, and gradually using Lilith’s succubus magic to stimulate her from afar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bit by bit, her hidden desires begin to surface as you carefully guide her down a path of temptation and pleasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Chiho’s desire peaks, you can take things even further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As her Lust Mark value increases, you’ll unlock new succubus abilities and seductive gameplay mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch as Chiho gradually loses control! Her innocent facade begins to crack as she starts taking the initiative herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Until eventually… things spiral far beyond what anyone could have imagined.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Chiho’s descent continues, new locations will become available, including the night market, izakaya bar, and hot spring inn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As her transformation progresses, Chiho begins to send you increasingly provocative selfies…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟Game Play💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this simulation game, you have 90 days to guide the heroine down a path of corruption. Each day is divided into four time slots: morning, afternoon, evening, and midnight. During each time slot, you can choose different actions such as working part-time to earn money, interacting with Chiho, or purchasing items. The game also features a variety of mini-games that help boost intimacy and advance the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/26f3bb02ab602966d7ea328c800bfa60.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/509a5c205352596f390cb0b52c3d06a1.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/509a5c205352596f390cb0b52c3d06a1.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/509a5c205352596f390cb0b52c3d06a1.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/a6d2f0acc5cabf6b0eadb78c6423e3a2.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/a6d2f0acc5cabf6b0eadb78c6423e3a2.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/a6d2f0acc5cabf6b0eadb78c6423e3a2.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/458ab18539e0857593eaaa6219168603.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/458ab18539e0857593eaaa6219168603.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/458ab18539e0857593eaaa6219168603.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work part-time, you can earn money to purchase powerful items that help advance the story. For example, the Spy Cam allows you to peek into the room of the newlywed couple next door, while the Ninja Scroll unlocks special gameplay features. As Chiho's corruption energy continues to accumulate, players can unlock more Devil Skills, leading to new interactions and story developments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/cfa1047ba9e75ab3ed66047b2a715a50.avif?t=1776137873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras_big/cfa1047ba9e75ab3ed66047b2a715a50.webp?t=1776137873 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/ab55145d78c902436ea311b4cd1806f9.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=2773 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/e4d2e0fdaafc9c6e7145d9d3669bb133.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/9fe68e3a5bf37e8a44df45be2e2033ff.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f4141ebe70e4b7182357d9d45ab95b3c.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1560 height=1040 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟Story💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Ryunosuke, a young landlord, and you've just leased your property out to a newlywed couple. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chiho and Shota have been together since university. While Shota keeps hitting walls at work, only bringing home a modest income, the couple support each other and do their best to enjoy their sweet newlywed life. However, you can feel your heart pounding and blood rushing the moment you set eyes on Chiho. You’re struck by her voluptuous bust, perfectly curvy figure, and her innocent untainted smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the couple hesitates after hearing the rent amount, you casually make a bold proposal: “How about letting Chiho clean my room to make up for the rent difference?” The couple agrees, and your daring arrangement begins to unfold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite having been called the &quot;legendary seducer&quot;, the bond between Chiho and Shota holds firm. At a loss, you turn to Lilith, a mischievous succubus who has long been irritated by Chiho’s naive purity and together, you strike a pact. With Lilith’s magic, you’ll attempt to awaken Chiho’s suppressed desires over 90 days, guiding her on a journey where pleasure and temptation blur the line between loyalty and lust.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And so, the 90-day countdown begins...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/21c11926e5d4689fa7ff2736c1dc3985.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💟Features💟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What begins as a simple housekeeping visit soon becomes something far more intimate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take every chance to interact with Chiho! Start with playful teasing, and gradually using Lilith’s succubus magic to stimulate her from afar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bit by bit, her hidden desires begin to surface as you carefully guide her down a path of temptation and pleasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/751d7de6b6f52dd66121f0e52dec9f13.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Chiho’s desire peaks, you can take things even further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As her Lust Mark value increases, you’ll unlock new succubus abilities and seductive gameplay mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch as Chiho gradually loses control! Her innocent facade begins to crack as she starts taking the initiative herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Until eventually… things spiral far beyond what anyone could have imagined.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/f65d2084f02d4230bb403f2dadb7ad7f.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/98ef3b482a01851cc065448c16d715db.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Chiho’s descent continues, new locations will become available, including the night market, izakaya bar, and hot spring inn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As her transformation progresses, Chiho begins to send you increasingly provocative selfies…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/331609ad40007495076a6e18c0a7f582.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/81a2372c8b13e9763efef423eb44993c.mp4?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.poster.avif?t=1776137873\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412290/extras/8d717f998d3da5dae309ceec2f392559.webm?t=1776137873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as